room_title: Escape room "The Mad Hatter" by Epic Escape Rooms in Valdosta
room_description:
You heard the wail of the tornado coming but after that, everything went hazy... As the storm settles, it becomes clear you are no longer in Valdosta but, where? Before long you meet your "unique" host in this strange place and he informs you that no one actually ever leaves Wonderland!
Being a little crazy and loving a good twist, the Hatter agrees to allow you to go home if you can complete a series of his challenges and puzzles. If you can't solve it all in less than 60 minutes - you will be stuck in Wonderland forever!
